        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 1: MLCK (MYLK) partially co-localizes with presynaptic marker SYT1 in immunofluorescence stainings. The imaging resolution does not enable a more specific annotation than \"synapse\".. Experimental description: M&M: \"Dissociated cultures of hippocampal CA1-CA3 neurons were prepared from postnatal day 0 rats as described previously with minor modifications\"\n\nantibody:\nanti-MLCK polyclonal antibody (Covance, Princeton, NJ)" ;
